						               													<description>On the quiet mining world of Keshen III, miners and colonial militia have begun defecting and opening fire on loyal security forces. Meanwhile, unidentified military ships are descending from orbit.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Welcome to the first Solo Challenge for the Renegade Scout miniatures rules.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This offers an infantry assault scenario that can be played on your own or with a friend cooperating to &amp;quot;solve&amp;quot; the scenario. You can use any force you like, with the aim being to beat the scenario using the smallest possible points value.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     You need 14 infantry figures for the enemy forces. Your own force can be as large or small as you like with 200-250 points (using the Army Builder) being a good starting point. &amp;#10;     Mechanics for solo play are included. &amp;#10;     3 difficulty toggles are provided to bolster the enemy forces. &amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The scenario is well suited to help learning the rules, experimenting with different forces and exercising your army building muscles.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
